title: Andarta - Blue J-Dish Cloths - Pack of 50 (35 x 42cm) - Versatile Cleaning Cloths for Kitchens, Bathrooms and General Areas - Absorbent, Quick-Drying, Washable and Lightweight
features: ALL PURPOSE - Our J-Dish Cloths are suitable for any tasks requiring effective cleaning and wiping. The cloths can be used on various surfaces across the home or business, for all your cleaning needs. Whether you're tackling everyday spills or tough messes, these cloths are up to the task. (Colour: Blue, Size: Pack of 50, 35 x 42cm)

VERSATILE CLOTH - Our J-Dish Cloths provide effortless dirt removal, making cleaning a breeze. Designed for a wide range of uses, including kitchen cleaning, bathroom cleaning, dusting, general cleaning, mopping up spills, vehicle cleaning, industrial and commercial use.

HIGHLY ABSORBENT - With excellent absorbency, these cloths help minimise drips and streaks, leaving surfaces dry and streak-free. They also ensure efficient cleanup by quickly soaking up liquids and spills.

SINGLE USE OR REUSABLE - These cloths are perfect for short-term or single-shift use - ideal for any cleaning job. Simply put them in the washing machine for a fresh start or dispose of them after use.

HYGIENIC PRODUCT - Our quick-drying cloths help to prevent the spread of germs by effectively removing bacteria and germs from surfaces, reducing the risk of cross-contamination. Each pack is wrapped in plastic packaging to ensure maximum hygiene upon receipt of product.
